content:
I apologize for the oversight. Here are the suggested tempos for each song in this imaginary techno/house/dub album:

1. "Mystic Rhythms" - 120-128 BPM (beats per minute)
2. "Wizard's Fury" - 128-136 BPM
3. "Sorcery Dub" - 75-85 BPM
4. "Enchanted Groove" - 105-115 BPM
5. "Wise One's Way" - 85-95 BPM
6. "Sage's Journey" - 95-105 BPM

I hope these tempos are helpful in your creative process. Remember that the tempo of a song can have a big impact on its overall feel and energy, so it's worth considering how you want each song to feel and what tempo will help you achieve that. Experiment with different tempos and see what works best for your music! If you have any further questions or need more guidance, don't hesitate to ask.
